{"tid":1955394,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一間中伏餐廳 好食是良知","createTime":"2020-04-02T12:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T17:53:02.000Z","uid":20115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14f40622fd46ae6a9588813ad5e5799a4d6dd4bc","tid":1955394,"uid":20115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:24:46.000Z","msg":"唔知附近有咩好食 見呢間野有連豬咪入去買野食試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到呢間茶記同我講 成間餐廳得4個餐選擇 <br />\n要左個咖喱雞意粉 58 外賣加2 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後番到去打開嚟睇 3隻雞尖 一舊仔雞肉 雞翼半邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪撚同我再講黃黃黃 咁既質素搵撚食"},{"pid":"24d1f84ad39af3bbbe005426e0be4d4fa7919384","tid":1955394,"uid":177620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"藍都可以難食，黃都有好食嘅<br />\n但寧願食難食黃都唔食好食藍"},{"pid":"0712f081e56564035f67d5115bfb2742ed6f045d","tid":1955394,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"長洲黃店熾工房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed7802723a564b952478434ca0026c43a148a90","tid":1955394,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:51:38.000Z","msg":"消費者唔係傻，呢啲難食黃店好快會被淘汰，唔使嬲"},{"pid":"1433d77eafe0752238defba8d0593ac28ae18f39","tid":1955394,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}